nodes.text: A male poacher was active during the Galactic Civil War. Sometime prior to 4 ABY, the poacher, in an attempt to pay of his debts for the crime lord Jabba Desilijic Tiure, kidnapped four Yuzzum from the moon of Endor. However, when the poacher tried to give the Yuzzem to Jabba, the crime lord was infuriated and dropped the poacher and his catch into his rancor pit. The poacher was killed by the rancor.
